{"tid":1743132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[百屌成才] 建制「止暴制亂」失敗，投白票 / 投建制對家比返壓力建制！","createTime":"2019-11-21T05:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T07:03:25.000Z","uid":43327,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c312dfd42fc5b877885d0776290b126eafb731ad","tid":1743132,"uid":43327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"賓仔賓仔，細佬我真心支持左建制好多年，但見到佢地呢幾個月，警察日日上前線，佢地完全無出黎幫手止暴制亂，真心覺得佢地無用。大佬，泛民果班，日日仆出黎企前線幫d黑衫擋子彈，咁建制呢？有冇幫警察出過一句聲？冇去過前線都算，連送水送物資同警察打氣打無做，甚至唔再搞撐警集會，我屋企老豆老母就係黑衫害死既，我一定唔會投建制派！！<br />\n<br />\n呢班人仲想用止暴制亂食人血饅頭，含家產啦！！"},{"pid":"5efb9bab12261a6ef9afff30d90acb33cbf3d6f2","tid":1743132,"uid":43327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"一票不投建制派，建制派應該總辭！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a7461f609556251e3e65f6ef69e555898227b3","tid":1743132,"uid":301507,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"有票梗係投民建聯工聯會啦！<br />\n止暴製亂全靠佢地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf1add70f375e08c017f197b34382c370d45a51","tid":1743132,"uid":43327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"重要 post 冇人理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a277dad31e3aadd205cb41063c27c83c988ca39","tid":1743132,"uid":144084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"幫手推翻今個星期主線︰<br />\n團結！用你一票絕殺保皇黨 ! <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1737525/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1737525/</a>"},{"pid":"500631ae85bae09239f22da0e5ddd883a679bb0c","tid":1743132,"uid":43327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:50:14.000Z","msg":"一票不投建制派，建制派應該總辭！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11185120a34bb9f733c5e9e3a4de7a41ca25805","tid":1743132,"uid":122275,"like":0,"d